      "index": 2,
      "text": "And the evacuation efforts are proceeding on Guldra, although our transport ability is too limited for what is required, Sumire.\n\nThat's also why I asked for the <i>Argo</i>, we can use its cargo bays to temporarily house and transport refugees to Coromodir.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "But that's not our mission?",
          "conditions": null,
